{
  "stem": "888.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then we ate a little later, you know, just ourselves, you know, the two older boys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But otherwise, you know, between 12:30 and 1:00 o'clock, you know, we used to all sit down and eat, eat lunch, what we called the mittag, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, it was quite eventful, because there was not only us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there was always a cousin or two, or a guest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if somebody came to the door and asked for, you know, if we could spare-- you know, so they ask him to sit down, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So actually, there was always about 12, 13, 14, or 15 just on an average day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, of course, also in the morning, if people came to the door, and asked for-- you know, they want to have breakfast, and you know, they served them breakfast.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, all the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they didn't come--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were mainly people from other towns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were sort of beggars, you know, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or, they came for money, or they came, or they asked you for-- you know, to have, if they wanted something to eat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean-- you know, like for instance-- I mean, you know, like on a Saturday, on a holiday, people were invited.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, like for instance after temple, if somebody came over to my father and said, can you spare lunch, or whatever, he would invite them to the house, one or two people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were sat at the table.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were served like everybody else, you know, and included into conversation and different things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then of course, you know, there was always, you know, like students who were in--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the yeshiva, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
